-- Weakening for weakenings

opaque

  -- A definitional weakening lemma for weakenings.

  defn-wkWkʷ : ξ » ∇′ ⊇ ∇ → ∇ » ρ ∷ʷ Δ ⊇ Γ → ∇′ » ρ ∷ʷ Δ ⊇ Γ
