    app-subst (defn-wkRedTerm ξ⊇ t⇒t′) (defn-wkTerm ξ⊇ ⊢a)
  defn-wkRedTerm ξ⊇ (β-red ⊢A ⊢t ⊢x eq ok) =
    β-red (defn-wk ξ⊇ ⊢A)
          (defn-wkTerm ξ⊇ ⊢t)
          (defn-wkTerm ξ⊇ ⊢x)
          eq ok
